title: The Good Sisters [2009 - USA] indie occult horror
description:
The Good Sisters (2009 - USA)

Drama / Horror / Thriller

Production Company: Forbidden Pictures
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1215064/


Budget: $100,000 estimated

Breanne Good and Kindra Good are sisters with a secret life, being practitioners of witchcraft, glamours, and black magick. Fiercely protective of their privacy, craft, and ancient bloodline, they become suspicious of their new neighbour Daniel who also leads a life shrouded in mystery. Unsure if he is unnaturally obsessed with them, or if they are only being paranoid, the Good Sisters will have to draw all their power about them as it becomes clear their ages-old battle of good versus evil, light versus dark, freedom versus oppression, may be about to begin again. Which leaves the question . . . who is being Good, and who is not?
